{"tid":1421342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，有野想請教","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:24:39.000Z","uid":270549,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e4805f735a84d7714e5ebde287ee26f493afc0","tid":1421342,"uid":270549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMbCRWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMbCRWy.png&h=d782a685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車係馬路行 正確（冇理解錯啊）<br />\n你們點解可以吾比車過？<br />\n有咩特權？<br />\n仲要捉人落車打？ 打爛人架車 你們會有報應<br />\n <br />\n你們自己要在馬路上整路障，吾撚知係邊個比權你咁做  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚岩啊你們 暴徒正一暴徒</span><br />\n<br />\n人地比你們打完 打爛車 吾通吾上車走啊？<br />\n<br />\n又話人用車撞你 撞到邊個啊<br />\n<br />\n吾撚係你地站出馬路，攔住架車唔俾架車走啊<br />\n<br />\n請暴徒快啲死"},{"pid":"9ba69ac93a4dbaf6d756c113db4e59442906efba","tid":1421342,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"呢d咪叫天堂有路你不走。地獄無門走入黎囉"},{"pid":"1b831d088a0e0703567bb5e025b2beb3c1029a90","tid":1421342,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"吾你老母 p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833c3cee44e092ff58d97d62d0f29e9218bd27f3","tid":1421342,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"看圖說故事"},{"pid":"450031b8e57ea76fdfbd84efc7a061568a1b834f","tid":1421342,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廣東落黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"f1e02fdd7292b1f873001373d6b5bae0a4e6c8ec","tid":1421342,"uid":269805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"建議你看圖說故事之前做下fact check先衝出黎。<br />\n紅媒01都有交代<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/448747665308662/posts/1247651542084933?s=696675685&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F448747665308662%2Fposts%2F1247651542084933%3Fs%3D696675685%26sfns%3Dmo&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXChZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=24f2d8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/448747665308662/posts/1247651542084933?s=696675685&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n首先架車快速u turn<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/155843_9400c6674b52846414e349276256aaf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F155843_9400c6674b52846414e349276256aaf3.png&h=57a218f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撞低左一個站在旁邊的紅衫路人，以佢速度有理由相信佢係有心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/155844_72ce51a7d367d2f7f15cae53a5acec28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F155844_72ce51a7d367d2f7f15cae53a5acec28.png&h=004c1613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後佢想不顧而去，hit and run，先有班人截住佢，捉佢落車綁住，其間亦無證據顯示佢畀人打。佢其後扮有野要上車拎，點知上車就想偷走，所以畀人敲車再欄截。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/155846_a76b284f849d7039496b972a451a0aa1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F155846_a76b284f849d7039496b972a451a0aa1.png&h=2805d787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機完全不顧危險踩行油衝出去，隨時撞死人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/155849_a4825a42c9b0f591aad78093305a1f1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F155849_a4825a42c9b0f591aad78093305a1f1e.png&h=cc0efd4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b8ca054fffdff3d6433979737ba39de0bf3098f","tid":1421342,"uid":270549,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f4e4805f735a84d7714e5ebde287ee26f493afc0","tid":1421342,"uid":270549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited